INSIGHTS:

1: Women are more likely to buy than a man (~65%)
2: Maharashtra, Karnataka and Uttar Pradesh are the top 3 states (~35%)
3: Adult age group (30-49) is purchasing the most (~50%)
4: Amazon, flipkart, Myntra are the top contributing channel (~80%)

Conclusion:

Women customers above the age of 30 and below the age 50 should be targeted from states of Maharashtra, Kurnataka or Uttar Pradesh by showing ads/offers available on Amazon, flipkart and Myntra.
